From: Dave Stevenson <dave.stevenson@raspberrypi.org>
Date: Thu, 1 Mar 2018 11:02:44 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 49/80] dtoverlay: Add V4L2 decode to the bcm2835-codec
 overlay.

With encode mainly working, add decode.

Signed-off-by: Dave Stevenson <dave.stevenson@raspberrypi.org>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/overlays/bcm2835-codec-overlay.dts | 6 +++++-
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/overlays/bcm2835-codec-overlay.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/overlays/bcm2835-codec-overlay.dts
index 59ec0dbbc043..4c621ed05403 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/overlays/bcm2835-codec-overlay.dts
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/overlays/bcm2835-codec-overlay.dts
@@ -12,10 +12,14 @@
 	fragment@0 {
 		target = <&soc>;
 		__overlay__ {
-			v4l2: v4l2 {
+			v4l2_encode: v4l2_encode {
 				compatible = "raspberrypi,bcm2835-v4l2-encoder";
 				status = "okay";
 			};
+			v4l2_decode: v4l2_decode {
+				compatible = "raspberrypi,bcm2835-v4l2-decoder";
+				status = "okay";
+			};
 		};
 	};
 
